items.title: Awesome Zsh Plugins
items.content_text:
### Themes / [superconsole](https://github.com/alexchmykhalo/superconsole) - Windows-only

*   [bigyls (⭐3)](https://github.com/Bigyls/Bigyls-zsh-theme) - Based on [lpha3cho (⭐46)](https://github.com/sdcampbell/lpha3cho-Oh-My-Zsh-theme-for-pentesters). Includes decorators for date, time, IP address, `git` status, plugins and current directory.
*   [parrot-htb (⭐0)](https://github.com/Lloyd-Leo/parrot-htb-zsh-theme) - Includes decorators for current directory, `git` status and username\@hostname.
items.content_html:
